com.amazonaws.services.s3.transfer

Interface ObjectTaggingProvider


  • public interface ObjectTaggingProvider
    This is the callback interface which is used by TransferManager.uploadDirectory(String, String, File, boolean, ObjectMetadataProvider, ObjectTaggingProvider) and TransferManager.uploadFileList(String, String, File, List, ObjectMetadataProvider, ObjectTaggingProvider). The callback is invoked for each file that is uploaded by TransferManager and given an opportunity to specify the tags for each file.
